<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Confirm Your Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4c11 0%, #b027a9 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      .header .icon {
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #333;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .confirmation-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 25px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }
      .confirmation-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .alternative-link {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        word-break: break-all;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6c757d;
      }
      .info-box {
        background-color: #e7f3ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6c757d;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .security-notice {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
        color: #856404;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="icon">✉️</div>
        <h1>Confirm Your Email</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello!</h2>
        <p>
          We welcome you onboard to SmartPay, your go-to platform for purchasing
          products and paying later. To get started, we need to verify your
          email address.
        </p>

        <p>
          To complete your registration and activate your account, please
          confirm your email address by entering the One-Time Password (OTP)
          below:
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <p>Here's your confirmation OTP</p>
          <strong style="font-size: 24px; color: #333"><%= otp %></strong>
          <br />
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <strong>Why do we need email confirmation?</strong><br />
          Email confirmation helps us ensure that we can reach you with
          important updates and keeps your account secure.
        </div>

        <div class="security-notice">
          <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This confirmation OTP will expire in
          <%= expirationTime || '24 hours' %> for security reasons. If you
          didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email.
        </div>

        <p>Once you confirm your email, you'll be able to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access all platform features</li>
          <li>Receive important notifications</li>
          <li>Connect with other users</li>
          <li>Customize your profile settings</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or need help, don't hesitate to contact our
          support team.
        </p>

        <p>Welcome aboard!</p>
        <p><strong>The SmartPay Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to <strong><%= email %></strong></p>
        <p>
          If you didn't sign up for an account, you can safely ignore this
          email.
        </p>
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SmartPay. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
